      "review_title": "Man, people are dumb.",
      "review_description": "Yes, it would be cool if you could livestream on Twitch using this, and maybe such will be implemented one day. However, that is not the purpose of this app in its current state, and one should not assume such. Rating this application one star because of said assumption is foolish. This is a client for viewing Twitch content, much like the YouTube app is a client for viewing YouTube content. This suits the large majority of users. And it works well in that regard. The interface is relatively sleek, it performs well, and overall I deem it to be a good step for traditional, 2D applications on HorizonOS.",
